1
00:00:09,410 --> 00:00:10,240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}JACK-OF-ALL-TRADES, PARTY OF NONE</font>

2
00:00:10,530 --> 00:00:17,790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}JACK-OF-ALL-TRADES, PARTY OF NONE</font>

3
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:45,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sophia, Logan, Caroline...</font>

4
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They all have pretty heavy pasts.</font>

5
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially...</font>

6
00:01:51,250 --> 00:01:55,340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}EPISODE 10: THE JACK-OF-ALL-TRADES
MAKES THEM TRAIN HARD</font>

7
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selma-cchi, new lieutenant,</font>

8
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">morning!</font>

9
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

10
00:01:57,890 --> 00:01:59,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning...</font>

11
00:01:59,830 --> 00:02:00,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your desk...</font>

12
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...is as messy as ever.</font>

13
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:07,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's cleaner than usual today.</font>

14
00:02:07,010 --> 00:02:08,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is?</font>

15
00:02:08,490 --> 00:02:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're scaring
the new lieutenant, Estella.</font>

16
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I do my job right at least.</font>

17
00:02:13,850 --> 00:02:16,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Carla with the Adventure 
Management Division.</font>

18
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you.</font>

19
00:02:17,580 --> 00:02:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carla's looking after the new members.</font>

20
00:02:20,290 --> 00:02:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's like their caretaker.</font>

21
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

22
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you.</font>

23
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard from Estella that you'll 
be helping train Group 10.</font>

24
00:02:30,210 --> 00:02:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

25
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you read their files?</font>

26
00:02:33,790 --> 00:02:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did.</font>

27
00:02:35,510 --> 00:02:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only then did I make my decision.</font>

28
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then there's no need
for me to say anything.</font>

29
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please take care of them.</font>

30
00:02:43,980 --> 00:02:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will.</font>

31
00:02:45,260 --> 00:02:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were pretty worried about them.</font>

32
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you're looking 
out for them, Or-cchi.</font>

33
00:02:52,330 --> 00:02:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... "Or-cchi?"</font>

34
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? You don't want me calling 
you that in my head?</font>

35
00:02:57,360 --> 00:03:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it doesn't bother me, but...</font>

36
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what's the policy for training them?</font>

37
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None.</font>

38
00:03:03,820 --> 00:03:05,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're in charge of everything.</font>

39
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just teach them what you've 
learned from your experiences.</font>

40
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teach them what they need to know.</font>

41
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:17,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What they need...</i></font>

42
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine for him
to come up with the plan,</font>

43
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you could at least give him a goal.</font>

44
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

45
00:03:25,260 --> 00:03:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it'd be nice to have them able to</font>

46
00:03:27,170 --> 00:03:30,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">handle the middle floors on 
their own after six months.</font>

47
00:03:30,730 --> 00:03:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a pretty high bar.</font>

48
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We do have high expectations for them.</font>

49
00:03:35,100 --> 00:03:38,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They grew up a lot during 
the teaching expedition.</font>

50
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's certainly possible, but...</font>

51
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're counting on you, new lieutenant.</font>

52
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun.</font>

53
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you read the files...</font>

54
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know about me
and Sophia already, right?</font>

55
00:03:58,380 --> 00:04:01,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I was surprised, honestly.</font>

56
00:04:01,810 --> 00:04:04,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her mother was a maid in my household.</font>

57
00:04:04,780 --> 00:04:07,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She died right after giving birth to her.</font>

58
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After that, my family, 
the Claudels, took her in,</font>

59
00:04:13,620 --> 00:04:17,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but as the child of a mistress, 
she had no real place in the household.</font>

60
00:04:17,210 --> 00:04:20,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Life was hard for her at a young age.</font>

61
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did everything I could for her, but...</font>

62
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Things got even worse
for her after you left.</font>

63
00:04:29,050 --> 00:04:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

64
00:04:30,350 --> 00:04:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I came home for the 
first time after leaving...</font>

65
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I asked her...</font>

66
00:04:37,900 --> 00:04:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Why don't you come with me?"</font>

67
00:04:46,130 --> 00:04:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's why I want Sophia 
to become a great adventurer.</font>

68
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe you think it's wrong to give 
her special treatment, but...</font>

69
00:04:54,130 --> 00:04:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's only natural to feel the way you do.</font>

70
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do everything I can.</font>

71
00:04:58,160 --> 00:05:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to hear that.</font>

72
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care of my sister, Orhun.</font>

73
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Got it.</font>

74
00:05:08,490 --> 00:05:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mister!</font>

75
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun!</font>

76
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

77
00:05:12,890 --> 00:05:13,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

78
00:05:13,990 --> 00:05:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kept you all waiting, huh?</font>

79
00:05:17,260 --> 00:05:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know why I'm here?</font>

80
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. You're taking us on 
as students, right?</font>

81
00:05:24,290 --> 00:05:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is officially part 
of my work at the clan...</font>

82
00:05:27,390 --> 00:05:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I suppose you're right.</font>

83
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:30,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

84
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:34,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy you'll be teaching us again.</font>

85
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:38,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know all kinds of stuff 
and you're super-strong!</font>

86
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I've still got a lot 
to do to get stronger.</font>

87
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not true!</font>

88
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:44,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You totally beat up that Black Dragon!</font>

89
00:05:45,410 --> 00:05:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Totally beat it up, huh?</i></font>

90
00:05:47,650 --> 00:05:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>From my perspective, it was a close thing.</i></font>

91
00:05:51,810 --> 00:05:52,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

92
00:05:53,290 --> 00:05:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But someday, you'll have to fight 
the Black Dragon yourselves.</font>

93
00:05:58,130 --> 00:06:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to try and 
clear the Great Dungeon.</font>

94
00:06:00,650 --> 00:06:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have to fight the Black Dragon...?</font>

95
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know it would be hard for you right now,</font>

96
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I think you could do it someday.</font>

97
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've all got a lot of potential.</font>

98
00:06:12,010 --> 00:06:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With hard work, you can 
become great adventurers.</font>

99
00:06:15,930 --> 00:06:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do my best!</font>

100
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me too, of course!</font>

101
00:06:18,690 --> 00:06:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you for teaching us!</font>

102
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There're two important things I 
want to talk about at the start.</font>

103
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First,</font>

104
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:29,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you need to be thinking at all times.</font>

105
00:06:29,910 --> 00:06:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There're lots of different 
ways to solve any problem.</font>

106
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't just stick to the 
standard script. Be flexible.</font>

107
00:06:36,730 --> 00:06:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And secondly...</font>

108
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't think what I'm saying
is always right.</font>

109
00:06:41,210 --> 00:06:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't think you're always right?</font>

110
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does that mean?</font>

111
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know everything.</font>

112
00:06:48,990 --> 00:06:52,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made lots of mistakes and 
messed up a lot of things.</font>

113
00:06:52,660 --> 00:06:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't think that just because I'm your 
teacher, I'm automatically right.</font>

114
00:06:57,770 --> 00:06:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't just automatically do what I say.</font>

115
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think about it and make it part of 
your own knowledge and experiences.</font>

116
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're not sure, you can always ask.</font>

117
00:07:06,610 --> 00:07:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it?</font>

118
00:07:07,620 --> 00:07:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

119
00:07:08,770 --> 00:07:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, before we begin,</font>

120
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to hear why you decided 
to become adventurers.</font>

121
00:07:17,030 --> 00:07:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's start with Sophia.</font>

122
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay!</font>

123
00:07:20,770 --> 00:07:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be like my sister,
Selma Claudel.</font>

124
00:07:26,190 --> 00:07:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to decide for myself 
what it is I want to do...</font>

125
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like her...</font>

126
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:37,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She really looks up to 
Selma as a sister, huh?</i></font>

127
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I haven't really 
decided what I want to do.</font>

128
00:07:42,690 --> 00:07:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I became an adventurer, 
so I could find my own goals and dreams.</font>

129
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that's great.</font>

130
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll help too.</font>

131
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So let's search for your dream together.</font>

132
00:07:55,370 --> 00:07:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you, sir!</font>

133
00:07:57,840 --> 00:08:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was I showing off a little too much?</i></font>

134
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now it's your turn, Logan.</font>

135
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

136
00:08:03,050 --> 00:08:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reason I want to be an adventurer 
is that you can make a lot of money.</font>

137
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never heard that before.</font>

138
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. Keep going.</font>

139
00:08:12,430 --> 00:08:15,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The village I grew up in doesn't 
have good soil for growing.</font>

140
00:08:15,730 --> 00:08:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's barely enough food
to eat each day.</font>

141
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:24,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the villagers said it 
wasn't right for me to stay.</font>

142
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They gathered up all the money 
they had and sent me here.</font>

143
00:08:30,090 --> 00:08:35,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I want to become a successful 
adventurer and pay them back.</font>

144
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's my goal.</font>

145
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That's a wonderful reason.</font>

146
00:08:40,730 --> 00:08:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be honest, I thought I was as 
strong as a high-ranked adventurer.</font>

147
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But when I saw how strong you were,</font>

148
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and how scary the 
Black Dragon was, I realized...</font>

149
00:08:54,410 --> 00:08:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still weak.</font>

150
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need more power for my goals.</font>

151
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please!</font>

152
00:09:01,940 --> 00:09:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teach me everything I need 
to know to be an adventurer!</font>

153
00:09:08,450 --> 00:09:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

154
00:09:10,030 --> 00:09:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll teach you all I know.</font>

155
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's up to you to put 
in the effort to master it.</font>

156
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, thanks!</font>

157
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My turn, next!</font>

158
00:09:20,950 --> 00:09:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

159
00:09:22,060 --> 00:09:24,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you become
an adventurer, Caroline?</font>

160
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I...</font>

161
00:09:27,910 --> 00:09:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I don't have a real reason.</font>

162
00:09:32,090 --> 00:09:35,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess because I can kill monsters?</font>

163
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that will make everybody happy!</font>

164
00:09:39,090 --> 00:09:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? There's no other reason?</font>

165
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all, really!</font>

166
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just want everyone to smile!</font>

167
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:51,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really like people's smiles, huh?</font>

168
00:09:51,610 --> 00:09:53,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sure do, yeah!</font>

169
00:09:53,590 --> 00:09:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cause smiling people don't hit me!</font>

170
00:09:57,990 --> 00:10:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everybody's smiles disappear 
when monsters are around!</font>

171
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I kill them!</font>

172
00:10:04,610 --> 00:10:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want everyone to be smiling...</font>

173
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her darkness seems pretty deep.</font>

174
00:10:14,430 --> 00:10:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

175
00:10:15,970 --> 00:10:18,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's best that everyone smiles.</font>

176
00:10:18,010 --> 00:10:19,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for telling me.</font>

177
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're welcome!</font>

178
00:10:23,490 --> 00:10:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand why everyone 
decided to become adventurers.</font>

179
00:10:26,450 --> 00:10:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you all to keep those 
reasons in your head at all times.</font>

180
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:29,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it?</font>

181
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:31,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

182
00:10:31,230 --> 00:10:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, do you have a dream or a goal too?</font>

183
00:10:35,770 --> 00:10:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

184
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to make sure that no matter 
what horrible things happen,</font>

185
00:10:39,380 --> 00:10:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't lose anything...</font>

186
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be strong enough that I</font>

187
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can protect what matters to me
no matter what happens.</font>

188
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was why I became an adventurer.</font>

189
00:10:50,650 --> 00:10:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't protect anything if you're weak.</font>

190
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I plan on getting stronger too.</font>

191
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise you again.</font>

192
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:01,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be treating you like children.</font>

193
00:11:02,460 --> 00:11:05,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I want you to give me your all.</font>

194
00:11:05,890 --> 00:11:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

195
00:11:07,490 --> 00:11:09,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, sir.</font>

196
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:13,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Caroline, do you not like 
being called by a nickname?</font>

197
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't really care. Why?</font>

198
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The name "Caroline"
is pretty long, isn't it?</font>

199
00:11:20,190 --> 00:11:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems hard to say in an emergency.</font>

200
00:11:22,410 --> 00:11:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

201
00:11:24,250 --> 00:11:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then give me a wonderful name!</font>

202
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:28,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

203
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:31,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I want you to name me, Mister.</font>

204
00:11:34,570 --> 00:11:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay...</font>

205
00:11:36,140 --> 00:11:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Carol," maybe?</font>

206
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carol! I love it!</font>

207
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, my name is Carol!</font>

208
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:46,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's a nickname, not a name.</font>

209
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want a nickname, too!</font>

210
00:11:49,060 --> 00:11:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Logan" isn't that long, right?</font>

211
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please!</font>

212
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...</font>

213
00:11:57,010 --> 00:11:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Log"?</font>

214
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Log"...</font>

215
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The name Orhun gave me...</font>

216
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy!</font>

217
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it that moving?</i></font>

218
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I guess you could be Sophie?</font>

219
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it too obvious?</font>

220
00:12:16,030 --> 00:12:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I really like it.</font>

221
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sophie, huh?</font>

222
00:12:21,010 --> 00:12:23,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, we're Carol and Sophie, huh?</font>

223
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup!</font>

224
00:12:23,970 --> 00:12:27,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then can I call you "Teacher" from now on?</font>

225
00:12:28,900 --> 00:12:30,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind... I guess.</font>

226
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will too, then.</font>

227
00:12:34,050 --> 00:12:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll keep calling you "Orhun."</font>

228
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's totally fine.</font>

229
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:41,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's get to work.</font>

230
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

231
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

232
00:12:42,490 --> 00:12:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

233
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That fighting style is bad news.</i></font>

234
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A Defender shouldn't be 
trying to defeat an enemy.</i></font>

235
00:13:09,070 --> 00:13:13,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Their job is to just draw attention 
so the Attacker can finish the enemy.</i></font>

236
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:16,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the Attacker's job 
is the other way around.</i></font>

237
00:13:16,770 --> 00:13:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But right now, she's neither.</i></font>

238
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:24,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her fighting style has a very 
high risk of getting her killed.</i></font>

239
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carol!</font>

240
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's enough, I think.</i></font>

241
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reflective Wall.</font>

242
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Agility Up!</font>

243
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Triple!</font>

244
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's fast!</font>

245
00:13:42,300 --> 00:13:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carol.</font>

246
00:13:44,340 --> 00:13:47,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you're fighting, you need to 
keep an eye on your surroundings.</font>

247
00:13:47,860 --> 00:13:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew he'd come from the rear.</font>

248
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I was making sure 
I was defenseless, right?</font>

249
00:13:53,010 --> 00:13:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What does that mean?</i></font>

250
00:13:54,140 --> 00:13:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't understand.</i></font>

251
00:13:56,190 --> 00:13:59,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could've been badly hurt there.</font>

252
00:13:59,510 --> 00:14:01,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you dodge?</font>

253
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. I never told you, Teacher.</font>

254
00:14:12,130 --> 00:14:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you doing?</font>

255
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this her special ability?</i></font>

256
00:14:22,410 --> 00:14:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't die!</font>

257
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:27,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how hurt I get, 
I heal instantly.</font>

258
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm used to the pain, too!</font>

259
00:14:29,860 --> 00:14:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you don't have to worry!</font>

260
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Caroline Inglot...</i></font>

261
00:14:35,780 --> 00:14:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She was captured and held by 
the Cyclamen Church for years.</i></font>

262
00:14:40,420 --> 00:14:43,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Their goal is to revive the most powerful</i></font>

263
00:14:43,090 --> 00:14:46,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and terrifying of all monsters, 
the "Evil God."</i></font>

264
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They attack villages and towns,</i></font>

265
00:14:50,010 --> 00:14:53,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>conduct human experiments
and human trafficking.</i></font>

266
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're one of the largest 
criminal organizations.</i></font>

267
00:14:56,840 --> 00:15:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And two years ago, one of 
their bases was destroyed.</i></font>

268
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Albert from Unit 1 rescued her then.</i></font>

269
00:15:06,210 --> 00:15:09,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But the Church had done 
a lot of horrible things to her</i></font>

270
00:15:09,890 --> 00:15:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>because of her self-healing ability.</i></font>

271
00:15:13,290 --> 00:15:16,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She was extremely
mentally unstable, at the time.</i></font>

272
00:15:16,810 --> 00:15:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But after treatment, 
she recovered, to a degree.</i></font>

273
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She became an adventurer
of her own volition.</i></font>

274
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:27,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But the death of Albert, the man 
who saved her, came later...</i></font>

275
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The wounds in her heart 
are too deep to imagine.</i></font>

276
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:35,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I promised...</i></font>

277
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that I wouldn't treat them like children.</i></font>

278
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carol, look at your comrades' faces.</font>

279
00:15:47,800 --> 00:15:53,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? Why aren't they all smiling?</font>

280
00:15:53,130 --> 00:15:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you're hurt.</font>

281
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But my wounds...</font>

282
00:15:57,390 --> 00:16:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, they'll heal quickly.</font>

283
00:16:00,380 --> 00:16:02,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it still hurts, doesn't it?</font>

284
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you feel pain, me, Sophie, 
and Log all feel pain too.</font>

285
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because we care about our comrade.</font>

286
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So when you get hurt, we get 
hurt too, and lose our smiles.</font>

287
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that okay with you?</font>

288
00:16:19,660 --> 00:16:21,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! No it's not!</font>

289
00:16:21,860 --> 00:16:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should I do?!</font>

290
00:16:24,830 --> 00:16:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it.</i></font>

291
00:16:26,490 --> 00:16:31,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The scariest thing to her is 
to not see people smiling.</i></font>

292
00:16:32,380 --> 00:16:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So just don't do the things 
that cause you pain.</font>

293
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll never do it again, 
so smile, everyone!</font>

294
00:16:41,460 --> 00:16:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please!</font>

295
00:16:43,250 --> 00:16:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carol...</font>

296
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't hit me!</font>

297
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:50,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carol.</font>

298
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

299
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:58,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody here is going to hit you.</font>

300
00:17:00,570 --> 00:17:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anybody tried, I'd knock them out.</font>

301
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's fine.</font>

302
00:17:06,490 --> 00:17:08,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. It's fine.</font>

303
00:17:11,490 --> 00:17:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teacher...</font>

304
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

305
00:17:30,810 --> 00:17:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your movements still aren't right!</font>

306
00:17:32,610 --> 00:17:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They keep coming out of nowhere! 
It's hard to dodge them!</font>

307
00:17:37,380 --> 00:17:41,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carol, you want everyone to smile, right?</font>

308
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course!</font>

309
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:46,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So first you need to practice 
protecting yourself!</font>

310
00:17:46,910 --> 00:17:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No whining! Get to work!</font>

311
00:17:52,090 --> 00:17:53,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teacher, you meanie!</font>

312
00:17:57,600 --> 00:17:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your basics are getting better, Log.</font>

313
00:17:59,730 --> 00:18:04,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I didn't understand why I was using 
a spear instead of a sword at first.</font>

314
00:18:04,450 --> 00:18:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can keep your distance 
from an enemy with a spear,</font>

315
00:18:06,610 --> 00:18:08,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you can do double-duty 
as an Enchanter, right?</font>

316
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right! Smart thinking, teacher!</font>

317
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:13,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wil's better with a spear than I am.</font>

318
00:18:13,980 --> 00:18:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have him come teach you.</font>

319
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

320
00:18:19,250 --> 00:18:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">472, 465, 458...</font>

321
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Red!</font>

322
00:18:26,260 --> 00:18:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire Arrow!</font>

323
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">451, 444.</font>

324
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blue!</font>

325
00:18:33,460 --> 00:18:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Aqua Arrow!</font>

326
00:18:35,260 --> 00:18:38,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've got Sophia counting 
down from 500 by sevens,</i></font>

327
00:18:38,780 --> 00:18:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>while keeping two magic circles up</i></font>

328
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:43,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and casting spells at a target 
when random spells appear.</i></font>

329
00:18:43,860 --> 00:18:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's practice for parallel construction.</i></font>

330
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:48,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep counting.</font>

331
00:18:49,150 --> 00:18:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry!</font>

332
00:18:51,010 --> 00:18:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you stop moving or panic and mess up,</font>

333
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll put your comrades in danger.</font>

334
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right!</font>

335
00:18:58,570 --> 00:18:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two at once?!</font>

336
00:19:01,370 --> 00:19:02,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

337
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:07,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

338
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I reached out my hand without 
thinking and felt something strange.</font>

339
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strange?</font>

340
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

341
00:19:14,090 --> 00:19:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then the target fell over even 
though I didn't cast a spell.</font>

342
00:19:18,560 --> 00:19:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels like if I do this I can 
affect the things in front of me...</font>

343
00:19:24,610 --> 00:19:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I imagining things?</font>

344
00:19:26,580 --> 00:19:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt the same thing once,</font>

345
00:19:29,840 --> 00:19:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when my special ability appeared.</font>

346
00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's a special ability?</font>

347
00:19:33,130 --> 00:19:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like yours and my sister's?</font>

348
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it couldn't be...</font>

349
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's ability is different, 
and there's a lot we don't understand.</font>

350
00:19:41,890 --> 00:19:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So let's take our time and find 
out what that feeling really is.</font>

351
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

352
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}445.... 437...</font>

353
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If she's Selma's little 
sister, it's possible.</i></font>

354
00:19:51,890 --> 00:19:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, two more sets before we wrap up!</font>

355
00:19:54,010 --> 00:19:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

356
00:19:54,010 --> 00:19:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

357
00:19:54,700 --> 00:19:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Monster!</font>

358
00:19:59,510 --> 00:20:02,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun sure trained us hard.</font>

359
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Training's the one time 
he seems like a monster.</font>

360
00:20:06,760 --> 00:20:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, if it isn't Sophia and Caroline.</font>

361
00:20:11,720 --> 00:20:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Carla! Estella!</font>

362
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there.</font>

363
00:20:19,040 --> 00:20:22,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two seem to have really grown up, huh?</font>

364
00:20:22,570 --> 00:20:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're cheering you on!</font>

365
00:20:24,080 --> 00:20:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay! Thanks!</font>

366
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:27,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'll do my best.</font>

367
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Growing up, huh?</i></font>

368
00:20:31,310 --> 00:20:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I still haven't...</i></font>

369
00:20:36,730 --> 00:20:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Sophie?</font>

370
00:20:39,090 --> 00:20:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys are all so big...</font>

371
00:20:41,650 --> 00:20:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're still growing!</font>

372
00:20:44,260 --> 00:20:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll get bigger!</font>

373
00:20:48,260 --> 00:20:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Traitor.</font>

374
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't say that, Sophie!</font>

375
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, my...</font>

376
00:20:53,170 --> 00:20:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget it!</font>

377
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:04,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">353, 346, 339...</font>

378
00:21:04,450 --> 00:21:06,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire Arrow! Aqua Arrow!</font>

379
00:21:08,790 --> 00:21:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're both doing a lot better.</i></font>

380
00:21:14,290 --> 00:21:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking good. You're getting better.</font>

381
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

382
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:23,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yesterday, you defeated 
the floor boss on the 20th floor,</font>

383
00:21:23,230 --> 00:21:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Orc Lord, on your own.</font>

384
00:21:25,330 --> 00:21:27,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've passed the first stage.</font>

385
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going to aim higher from now on.</font>

386
00:21:31,870 --> 00:21:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hooray!</font>

387
00:21:34,260 --> 00:21:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun!</font>

388
00:21:39,020 --> 00:21:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your sword's ready.</font>

389
00:21:45,120 --> 00:21:48,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the one made from 
the Black Dragon's scale?</font>

390
00:21:48,130 --> 00:21:49,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

391
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The way it fits in my hand perfectly...</i></font>

392
00:21:52,670 --> 00:21:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And it's weighted just right.</i></font>

393
00:21:55,150 --> 00:21:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is my new sword...</i></font>

394
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:58,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

395
00:21:58,700 --> 00:22:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's perfect. I'm impressed!</font>

396
00:22:02,340 --> 00:22:04,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I swear on this sword...</i></font>

397
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that I'll protect my comrades 
no matter what!</i></font>

